data.description: There is truly room for everybody here!  This beautifully updated 6 bed 5 bath home is ready for any crowd! 5 bedrooms on 2nd floor, the primary has a fireplace and separate sitting area, along with a closet of dreams, and full bath with soaker tub.  The other 3 bedrooms are all attached to recently updated Jack/Jill bathrooms.  There is new flooring, paint and hardware throughout the home.  The kitchen is able to host every holiday and family gathering.  The super open concept allows for conversation and entertaining, yet still cozy for quiet family time too!  The finished basement has a great room and a non-conforming 7th bedroom or additional rec room. Specific storage areas, zoned HVAC, radon mitigation system and 3/4 bath.  The back yard is level, privacy fenced, new awning and no neighbors to the back.  Home also includes time lights.. guaranteed for life! Welcome Home!
